Class DatabaseTableModel<MODEL extends DBObject,DAO extends CrudDao<MODEL>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
      • javax.swing.table.DefaultTableModel
        • edu.neu.csye6200.model.DatabaseTableModel<MODEL,DAO>
  • Type Parameters:
    MODEL - Model Class which extends DBObject, e.g. Student
    DAO - Dao Class which extends CrudDao, e.g. StudentDao
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, javax.swing.table.TableModel

    public class DatabaseTableModel<MODEL extends DBObject,DAO extends CrudDao<MODEL>>
extends javax.swing.table.DefaultTableModel
    A generic table model to use with JTable or JXTable
    How to use:
     
     JTable table;
     DatabaseTableModel<Student, StudentDao> tableModel = new DatabaseTableModel<>(Student.class, StudentDao.class);
     table.setModel(tableModel);
     tableModel.refresh();
     tableModel.addEmpty();
     tableModel.delete(table, table.getSelectedRows());
    Author:
    Haotian Zheng
    See Also:
    StudentManagePanelController, Serialized Form
